'Users of this crystal structure: verify our intepretion of the electron density. Amplitudes and unmerged intensities are included with this deposition. Diffraction images will be deposited in a public repository. Geometry restraints for the fragment candidate were prepared with GRADE. The methyl group of the fragment candidate was not resolved by electron density and was omitted from the model. Ambiguous difference density suggests some form of covalent modification of Cys1147.'
